Privacy Notice
This Privacy Notice is effective as of August 18, 2023.
PLAYSTUDIOS US, LLC ("PLAYSTUDIOS", "we," "us" or "our") value your privacy. We offer a variety of games through various means, including mobile applications for iOS, Android and Amazon devices, online via websites, and on Facebook (collectively, our "Applications"). On our website www.PLAYSTUDIOS.com, (the "Site"), we provide information about our products and services, including those games, and how you may redeem certain points that you earn through the Applications. In this Privacy Notice ("Notice"), we describe how we collect, use, and disclose information that we obtain about visitors to our Site and our Applications, and the services offered on each (collectively, "Services").
By using any of our Services or visiting our Site or Applications, you acknowledge that your personal information will be handled as described in this Notice. Your use of our Site, Applications or Services, and any dispute over privacy, is subject to this Notice and our
Terms of Service
, including its applicable limitations on damages and the resolution of disputes. All capitalized terms used in this Notice and not defined within the Notice are defined in the Terms of Service.
When reading this Notice, "personal information" should be understood as "personal data" under the EEA / SWISS / UK residents section.
