10300 W. Charleston Blvd, Suite 13272
Las Vegas, NV 89135
Additional details about certain of these rights are provided below.
What happens if you request us to delete your personal information?
If you request to be forgotten, we will delete, put beyond use or anonymize your personal information such that you cannot be identified from the data that we retain, unless we have a basis to maintain it (see "How long will we store your personal information?").
Please know, however, that if you request to be forgotten and subsequently download and play any of our Applications, none of your historical performance data will be available, meaning you will lose any virtual currency, game progress, and Loyalty Points that you had at the time your request is processed.
What happens if you withdraw your consent for us to process your personal information?
If you withdraw your consent for us to process your personal information, we will treat your request as a request to be forgotten. We must take this action because when you play any of our Applications, whether via a mobile device or Facebook, we obtain and process personal information.
